content: Does anyone know anything about changes to the StructureDefinition resource in STU3. I'm not sure whether or not there should be "constrainedType" or just "type". Examples on /structuredefinition.html show "constrainedType" but the element/attribute table does not have "constrainedType", it only has "type".

look on the resource content tab 'R2 Diff'
Each resource has this tab in the content page for differences from DSTU2
